        <h2>Expert Witness Services:</h2>

        <p>A seasoned expert witness in patent litigation, Dr. Lavian brings <a href="/communications-expert-witness/">experience</a> in <a href="/about-dr-lavian/">academic and industrial research</a> and a Ph.D. from UC Berkeley specializing in <a href="/us-20180130102-reliable-rating-system-and-method-thereof/">telecommunications</a> and network <a href="/us-10348313-radar-target-detection-system/">communications</a> to his consulting work.</p>

        <p>His expertise extends to <a href="/communications-expert-witness/mobile-wireless-expert/">computer networks</a>, data communications, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">LAN/WAN, TCP/IP, UDP, VPN</a>, VoIP, streaming media, chat, SMS, <a href="/us-10598764-radar-target-detection-and-imaging-system-for-autonomous-car/">mobile wireless</a>, Ethernet, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/routing-switching-expert/">routing</a>, switching, Internet, and web techs. Dr. Lavian offers expert witness services in patent cases, including expert testimony, expert witness reports, and patent analysis of Internet techs, standards, and protocols.</p>

        <p>Moreover, he offers expert witness services and provides courtroom presence, clear testimony, and the ability to quickly distill complex concepts into the basics.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian has testified in Federal courts before judges and juries, the USPTO PTAB, and the ITC as a highly expert witness. He has supported Intellectual Property (IP) litigation cases related to over 140 patents in <a href="/us-20130080898-electronic-communications/">network communications</a> and telecommunications, including Internet Protocols (TCP/IP), streaming media, and mobile technologies. Cases involved leading companies such as Amazon, LinkedIn, Avaya, Netflix, T-Mobile, ZTE, Ericsson, Cisco Systems, Juniper Networks, Arista, Polycom, Motorola, LG, WhatsApp, Instagram, Microsoft, Google, Huawei, Facebook, Apple, Ericsson, and Netflix.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian has experience working with law firms, giving expert witness services, patent analysis, prior art, source code reviews, hardware reviews, patent infringement, patent invalidity, trade secrets, and other related matters.</p>

        <p>Therefore, he has <a href="/cases-expert-witness-testimony/">testified as an expert witness</a> over 70 times in depositions and trials and has written numerous expert reports. These reports comprise state-of-the-art research and tech analysis regarding patent claims, invalidity/validity, infringement/non-infringement, claim constructions, and prior art.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian presents technical material in plain English common sense and uses terminology understandable by technical and lay audiences alike.</p>

