        <h2>Expert Services</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Dr. Lavian is an expert in network communications and telecommunications. His extensive knowledge and expertise in these areas allow him to provide valuable insights and testimony in patent cases involving these topics. Dr. Lavian is also skilled at providing technical education for claim constructions and Markman hearings. This involves explaining the technical details of patents and other legal documents to judges and other legal professionals, helping them understand a case&rsquo;s technical aspects.</li>

          <li>Dr. Lavian has also written expert reports for a range of corporate clients. These reports typically include detailed analyses of the technical aspects of the case, definitions of key technical terms, and an explanation of the claim construction process. This helps to provide a clear and comprehensive understanding of the technical aspects of the case. Dr. Lavian&rsquo;s ability to communicate complex technical information to audiences with varying technical expertise is precious in this role.</li>

          <li>Dr. Lavian&rsquo;s expertise in network communications and telecommunications and his ability to communicate complex technical information effectively make him a valuable resource for corporate clients. Whether providing expert testimony in legal cases, offering technical education, or conducting technical analyses, Dr. Lavian is well-equipped to help companies and organizations navigate the complex world of technology and networking.</li>
